OL,3,CLast remaining pub in Bristol estate
OL,4,Csaved from demolition
OL,6,FThe last remaining pub in a Bristol
OL,7,Fhousing estate has been saved from
OL,8,Fdemolition.
OL,10,FThe Giant Goram, in Barrowmead Drive,
OL,11,FLawrence Weston, opened in the 1950s
OL,12,Fbut has been closed for several years.
OL,14,FIt was bought by Hawkfield Homes in
OL,15,F2019, which then applied to Bristol
OL,16,FCity Council for permission to knock
OL,17,Fit down and build eight houses and a
OL,18,Fmicropub there.
