OL,6,FThe plans have faced stiff opposition,
OL,7,Fwith campaigners saying the micropub
OL,8,Fwould only have space for a few
OL,9,Fcustomers and there are no other pubs
OL,10,Fnearby.
OL,12,FCommunity group 'Save The Giant Goram'
OL,13,Fis campaigning to buy it and reopen it.
OL,15,FBristol City Council's development
OL,16,Fcontrol A committee has now voted to
OL,17,Frefuse permission for the demolition.
