OL,6,FLabour Councillor Tom Blenkinsop,
OL,7,Frepresenting Avonmouth and Lawrence
OL,8,FWeston, added: "Lawrence Weston is one
OL,9,Fof the most deprived areas in Bristol
OL,10,Fand the United Kingdom, it needs all
OL,11,Fthe help it can get.
OL,13,F"I think there are better options that
OL,14,Fremain available."
OL,16,FChris Faulkner Gibson, from the
OL,17,FCampaign for Real Ale, said: "A
OL,18,Fmicropub will not meet the needs of
OL,19,Fthe local community.
OL,26,@yD@^OU
