OL,6,F"But a community-owned and operated
OL,7,Ffull-sized pub ` run on the Blunkett
OL,8,FFoundation's 'More than a Pub' model `
OL,9,Fmost certainly will."
OL,11,FThe key question was whether the tiny
OL,12,Fnew bar counted as "alternative
OL,13,Fprovision" to the existing Giant Goram.
OL,15,FCouncil policy says pubs can't be
OL,16,Fknocked down, unless there are
OL,17,Falternative ones within 800 metres or
OL,18,Fa 10-minute walk.
