OL,6,FDevelopers and a council planning
OL,7,Fofficer said the micropub counted as
OL,8,Fan alternative, but this was disputed
OL,9,Fby campaigners and councillors.
OL,11,FPaul Jobson, representing the
OL,12,Fdeveloper, said: "The proposal will
OL,13,Fdeliver a micropub which is considered
OL,14,Fa viable alternative for the former
OL,15,Fpublic house.
OL,17,F"Refusal will be difficult to justify
OL,18,Fand clearly challengeable at appeal.
OL,26,@tD@ROU
