OL,6,F"I would urge members to determine the
OL,7,Fapplication with their heads, rather
OL,8,Fthan perhaps their hearts."
OL,10,FThe developer is likely to appeal to
OL,11,Fthe government's Planning
OL,12,FInspectorate, who could overturn the
OL,13,Fcommittee's decision.
OL,15,FThis means that the battle for the
OL,16,FGiant Goram could drag on for several
OL,17,Fmore months yet.
