OL,6,FGreen Cllr Serena Ralston said:
OL,7,F"Technically a micropub is not a pub,
OL,8,Fin the sense that this community needs
OL,9,Fa pub.
OL,11,F"It's not going to provide those
OL,12,Fcommunity facilities that are so badly
OL,13,Fneeded. The evidence is not there, it
OL,14,Fjust doesn't stack up."
